OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy start to Easter Sunday
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier for a time as blustery
OL,8,Fshowers move east, these becoming
OL,9,Fisolated later with sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping into the early evening, and
OL,11,Fwinds slowly easing. Feeling cooler
OL,12,Fthan Saturday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny residual showers quickly
OL,15,Ffading to leave a dry night with long
OL,16,Fclear spells, and winds becoming
OL,17,Fgenerally light. Turning cold with a
OL,18,Fslight frost developing in many places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
