OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FStarting chilly with an early
OL,6,Fwidespread slight frost. A dry day to
OL,7,Ffollow with variable cloud but also
OL,8,Fbright spells at times. Generally
OL,9,Flight winds, with near average
OL,10,Fafternoon temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FChilly
OL,13,Fstart Tuesday, then fine with warm
OL,14,Fsunshine and breezier, but cooler
OL,15,Fwhere any onshore winds. Warm and
OL,16,Fbright Wednesday, cloudier later.
OL,17,FThursday, cooler and breezy with
OL,18,Fsunshine and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
